Package org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata

Class FabricMethodInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.MethodInfo<FabricParameterInfo>
      • org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata.FabricMethodInfo
  • public class FabricMethodInfo
extends MethodInfo<FabricParameterInfo>
    Holds additional information about a smart contract method.

    It is recommended to use FabricContractInfoBuilder to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    FabricContractInfoBuilder
